<main class="wrap">
  <h1 class="title reveal">Program — English</h1>
  <p class="lead reveal">Functional English for school and life — vocabulary, speaking confidence, and clear writing.</p>

  <section class="grid">
    <article class="card reveal"><h3>What we teach</h3><ul>
      <li>Vocabulary in themes (home, school, community).</li>
      <li>Pronunciation &amp; conversation basics.</li>
      <li>Writing: sentences → paragraphs → short emails.</li>
    </ul></article>
    <article class="card reveal"><h3>Activities</h3><ul>
      <li>Dialogue practice; role-plays; show-and-tell.</li>
      <li>Picture prompts; sentence builders.</li>
      <li>Mini presentations with simple slides.</li>
    </ul></article>
    <article class="card reveal"><h3>Outcomes</h3><ul>
      <li>More words, better phrases, clearer speech.</li>
      <li>Confidence in everyday interactions.</li>
      <li>Basic writing for school and messages.</li>
    </ul></article>
    <article class="card reveal"><h3>Who it’s for</h3><ul>
      <li>Primary to early secondary; mixed proficiency.</li>
    </ul></article>
  </section>

